            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-12" style="background-color: #282828;">
                    <ul style="text-align: justify; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 5px;">
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 10px; text-align:left; color:#9A9899;">
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    In Gridcoin's Proof-of-Stake (POS) system, rewards are minted as yearly compound interest <a href="http://wiki.gridcoin.us/Proof-of-Research#Proof-of-Stake">(Read more about POS)</a>.
                                </li>
                                <li style="padding-top:10px;">
                                    In order to mint yearly compound interest, a positive balance of GRC is required (This is the case for all POS cryptocurrencies).
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>
                                            There are 960 blocks per day that you can attempt to stake. If you've got 1% of the total Gridcoin supply, you'll approximately stake 9.6 blocks per day.
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            The formula required to work out the quantity of coins to stake in a period of time is:
                                            <ul>
                                                <li>
                                                    <code>
                                                    EstimatedDaysUntilStake=(1/(UserBalance/NetworkCoinSupply))/960
                                                    </code>
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <code>
                                                    CoinsRequired=(1/(days*960))*NetworkCoinSupply
                                                    </code>
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    Note: The payout window is approximately 182.5 days. This may (most likely will) increase in the future. 
                                                </li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            Best practice is to stake 24/7, since you have an opportunity to stake each block (even if your probability is low).
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                </li>
                                <li style="padding-top:5px;">
                                    To register your CPID in the DPOR system, you need to advertise a beacon to the network in the form of a smart transaction that costs a very small fee.
                                </li>
                                <li style="padding-top:5px;">
                                    The DPOR system utilizes ResearchAge to securely reward users on top of their minted blocks.
                                </li>
                                <li style="padding-top:5px;">
                                    Thusly, the rate at which you are rewarded for your BOINC work is identical to the rate at which you mint POS blocks (since you're rewarded for DPOR on top of your interest payment).
                                </li>
                                <li style="padding-top:5px;">
                                    Note: Your balance does not affect the magnitude calculation, only the rate of payment.
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
